public interface ServicePanelDef
extends Serializable

ServicePanelDef is the base type for definition beans of wicket components that provide user interface services.
Wicket service definitions are the means for information exchange between service client and service provider. They also act as keys used in order to locate the appropriate wicket service implementation.
ServicePanels execute actions provided by their clients. The providers may also provide a Flag for each action that indicates whether the current user is authorized to use the button. If Flag.isUp() returns true or Flag is null, the user is allowed to execute the action. Whether the buttons are disabled or show an error message when pressed for unauthorized users is controlled by the disableUnauthorizedButtons property.
